data.description: This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom beautiful home is located in a peaceful neighborhood. It offers spacious and well-though of design that provides comfortable living experience. You will be greeted by bright and spacious foyer that leads to the center of the home. The open concept design provides seamless transition between rooms, excellent for daily living and entertaining guests. High ceiling and large windows offer natural light , providing a welcoming ambience. For those for like to host outdoor gatherings or gardening, this property offers spacious backyard to do just that. The location offers easy access to amenities, shopping, parks and schools. This home offers style and peaceful atmosphere, making it an ideal place for anyone looking for just exactly that. Schedule your showing now!
